## 7. Integrao com PulseDaemon

```python
from neocortex.core.services.pulse_daemon import get_pulse_daemon
from neocortex.core.services.ttl_manager import get_ttl_manager

daemon = get_pulse_daemon()
ttl = get_ttl_manager()

# Registra hook para session timeout
daemon.register_hook('session_timeout', lambda data: ttl.cancel(data['session_id']))

# Configura TTL de sesso com refresh proativo
ttl.set_ttl(
    key=f"session:{session_id}",
    ttl=18000,
    callback=lambda: daemon.fire('session_timeout', {'session_id': session_id}),
    refresh_before=300
)
```

